title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) in Sudan 2024
yAxis: Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars
summary: In general Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.

Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars is gradually increasing from 1992 to 1993, roughly constant from 1993 to 1995, slightly increasing from 1995 to 1996, roughly constant from 1996 to 1999, and finally slightly increasing from 1999 to 2000.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 1999 and 2000.
The highest Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars, of value 13.13 was reached at Year 2000
Minimum Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars about 3.1 was reached at Year 1992
